Bike Lane Analysis

Types of Bike Lanes

There are three main categories of bike lanes in New York City’s bike lane data: Protected Lanes, Unprotected Lanes, and Sharrows. A fourth category, Combination, is comprised of the road segments with a combination of the other three bike lane categories.
